author: Charlotte Cox
title: Live: Major incident after 'suspicious package found' near tram stop
text:
Incident at Anchorage 2, Anchorage Quay (Photo: @m7leicauser) Share 
A building has been evacuated in Salford Quays after a suspicious package was found on the premises. 
Police, ambulance crews and fire services all remain at the scene after the alarm was raised at Anchorage 2, Anchorage Quay.Roads have been blocked off nearby as fire services search the building. 
A police spokesman said: "We were called shortly after 1.30pm to Anchorage Quay after a suspicious package was found. 
"Part of the building has been evacuated as a full search is conducted of the area." 
We will bring you the latest updates here. Key Events
